data.description: Traditional Colonial Saltbox located in popular Taylor Woods Subdivision. The covered front porch leads you into the surprisingly open floor plan. Island kitchen features stainless appliances & updated lighting. The family room features a vaulted ceiling with fan, wall of windows to the back, and a cozy gas fireplace. Home office with corner windows has potential to be a 4th bedroom. Utility room and a spacious dining area round out the 1st floor. Owner's suite has tons of natural light, and features a private bath & spacious closet. 2 other bedrooms share the 2nd full bath up. The finished lower level adds 250sqft of living space, and has its own full bath! The back yard is done right! There is a deck, patio & firepit, with an abundance of trees keeping  it private. New HVAC system '21.
